      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Norman Bender letter deplores fact that White House scandal will depress Democratic and undecided voters in November 3 elections</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
